=== Bigscreen Beyond x VRChat Storage Can ===
The [https://store.bigscreenvr.com/products/bigscreen-beyond-x-vrchat-storage-can Bigscreen Beyond x VRChat Storage Can] is a storage container which is designed to store the Bigscreen Beyond headset. This counterpart features VRChat branding and design elements around the can. This limited edition storage can was announced on February 6, 2024,<ref>[https://x.com/BigscreenVR/status/1754942807616454759 Excited to unveil the Bigscreen Beyond Storage Can] on X; retrieved July 17, 2025.</ref> and marks the first collaboration between VRChat and Bigscreen.